## v1.0.0 (2026-06-19)

**Initial version.** Created via merged PR #2591. Captured the planning learning: when an audit/lint NITPICK proposes renaming a file/symbol for discoverability, check if the name is a load-bearing cross-repo convention; document the rationale instead of renaming. The plan that produced it subsequently received a NOGO, prompting the v1.1.0 re-plan/correction.
